ll come to you to be kept alive."}, {:version=>"English Standard Version", :text=>"Of the birds according to their kinds, and of the animals according to their kinds, of every creeping thing of the ground, according to its kind, two of every sort shall come in to you to keep them alive."}, {:version=>"Berean Study Bible", :text=>"Two of every kind of bird and animal and crawling creature will come to you to be kept alive."}, {:version=>"New American Standard Bible ", :text=>"\"Of the birds after their kind, and of the animals after their kind, of every creeping thing of the ground after its kind, two of every kind will come to you to keep them alive."}, {:version=>"New King James Version", :text=>"Of the birds after their kind, of animals after their kind, and of every creeping thing of the earth after its kind, two of every "}, {:version=>" will come to you to keep ", :text=>" alive."}, {:version=>"King James Bible", :text=>"Of fowls after their kind, and of cattle after their kind, of every creeping thing of the earth after his kind, two of every "}, {:version=>" shall come unto thee, to keep ", :text=>" alive."}, {:version=>"Christian Standard Bible", :text=>"Two of everything--from the birds according to their kinds, from the livestock according to their kinds, and from the animals that crawl on the ground according to their kinds--will come to you so that you can keep them alive."}, {:version=>"Holman Christian Standard Bible", :text=>"Two of everything--from the birds according to their kinds, from the livestock according to their kinds, and from the animals that crawl on the ground according to their kinds--will come to you so that you can keep them alive. "}, {:version=>"International Standard Version", :text=>"From birds according to their species, from domestic animals according to their species, and from everything that crawls on the ground according to their species —two of everything will come to you so they may remain alive. "}, {:version=>"NET Bible", :text=>"Of the birds after their kinds, and of the cattle after their kinds, and of every creeping thing of the ground after its kind, two of every kind will come to you so you can keep them alive."}, {:version=>"New Heart English Bible", :text=>"Of the flying creatures after their kind, of the animals after their kind, and  of every crawling creature of the ground after their  kind, two of every sort shall come to you, to keep them alive."}, {:version=>"GOD'S WORD® Translation", :text=>"Two of every type of bird, every type of domestic animal, and every type of creature that crawls on the ground will come to you to be kept alive."}, {:version=>"JPS Tanakh 1917", :text=>"Of the fowl after their kind, and of the cattle after their kind, of every creeping thing of the ground after its kind, two of every sort shall come unto thee, to keep them alive."}, {:version=>"New American Standard 1977 ", :text=>"“Of the birds after their kind, and of the animals after their kind, of every creeping thing of the ground after its kind, two of every "}, {:version=>" shall come to you to keep ", :text=>" alive."}, {:version=>"King James 2000 Bible", :text=>"Of fowls after their kind, and of cattle after their kind, of every creeping thing of the earth after its kind, two of every sort shall come unto you, to keep them alive."}, {:version=>"American King James Version", :text=>"Of fowls after their kind, and of cattle after their kind, of every creeping thing of the earth after his kind, two of every sort shall come to you, to keep them alive."}, {:version=>"American Standard Version", :text=>"Of the birds after their kind, and of the cattle after their kind, of every creeping thing of the ground after its kind, two of every sort shall come unto thee, to keep them alive."}, {:version=>"Brenton Septuagint Translation", :text=>"Of all winged birds after their kind, and of all cattle after their kind, and of all reptiles creeping upon the earth after their kind, pairs of all shall come in to thee, male and female to be fed with thee."}, {:version=>"Douay-Rheims Bible", :text=>"Of fowls according to their kind, and of beasts in their kind, and of every thing that creepeth on earth according to its kind; two of every sort shall go in with thee, that they may live. "}, {:version=>"Darby Bible Translation", :text=>"Of fowl after their kind, and of the cattle after their kind, of every creeping thing of the ground after its kind, two of each shall go in to thee, to keep [them] alive."}, {:version=>"English Revised Version", :text=>"Of the fowl after their kind, and of the cattle after their kind, of every creeping thing of the ground after its kind, two of every sort shall come unto thee, to keep them alive."}, {:version=>"Webster's Bible Translation", :text=>"Of fowls after their kind, and of cattle after their kind, of every creeping animal of the earth after its kind, two of every sort shall come to thee, to keep them alive."}, {:version=>"World English Bible", :text=>"Of the birds after their kind, of the livestock after their kind, of every creeping thing of the ground after its kind, two of every sort shall come to you, to keep them alive."}, {:version=>"Young's Literal Translation", :text=>" Of the fowl after its kind, and of the cattle after their kind, of every creeping thing of the ground after its kind, two of every sort they come in unto thee, to keep alive."}]}